Reasoning: The paper deals with capacity analysis of multiple antenna systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). The investigation of high-SNR capacity also involves system-level analysis and optimization, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The use of local oscillators and phase noise also relates to networked systems and networking (cs.NI). Finally, the paper may also be relevant to multimedia systems and applications (cs.MM) as multiple antennas are often used in wireless multimedia communication.
